# reconf

Reconf is a program used to dynamically generate config (or other plain text) files using
[Handlebars]({{hb_url}}) templates for formatting and [Rhai]({{rhai_url}}) 
for generating template values and as Handlebars helpers.

This README was generated using the example profile.

Templating Features:

{{!-- This is a Handlebars comment! --}}
